STATE
v.
STUCKMAN 2019-0118 Supreme Court of Ohio. April 23, 2019

MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSAL

Appellant has not filed a memorandum in support of jurisdiction, due April 19, 2019, in compliance with the Rules of Practice of the Supreme Court of Ohio and therefore has failed to prosecute this cause with the requisite diligence. Cause dismissed.
